Subject: Re: Mystery oil leak

If it's really not the main seal or o-ring it could be
the cam plug. If it's neither then you might have a
cracked case. I've had a couple of cases crack and
they're tough to diagnose because the crack seems to
close up when the engine cools off.
Steve Elms
